      </div>
<p>The latest State of Play took place in April, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/borderlands-4-focused-state-of-play-takes-place-today-how-to-watch-and-what-to-expect/1100-6531223/" data-ref-id="1100-6531223">focused on Borderlands 4</a>. Before that, there was a 45-minute State of Play event in February featuring the <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/playstation-state-of-play-february-2025-all-the-biggest-announcements/2900-6256/#1" data-ref-id="2900-6256">debut of Ghost of Yotei</a>. There was no State of Play or Showcase event in June 2024, but Sony did hold a <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/state-of-play-may-2024-all-the-biggest-ps5-announcements-and-games/2900-5435/#1" data-ref-id="2900-5435">State of Play in May 2024</a> that showed off the ill-fated live-service game Concord and God of War Ragnarok for PC.</p><p>While Sony's plans for a summer showcase remain unknown, we do know that there will be more than a dozen summertime gaming events, including the recent <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/warhammer-skulls-2025-all-the-game-announcements-and-news/2900-6608/" data-ref-id="2900-6608">Warhammer Skulls showcase.</a> For more, check out <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/summer-game-conference-schedule-2025/1100-6531627/" data-ref-id="1100-6531627">GameSpot's full summer game conference schedule rundown</a> to find out what's happening when.</p><p>The next big PlayStation exclusive is<a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/death-stranding-2-story-theories-and-everything-we-know/1100-6516214/" data-ref-id="1100-6516214"> Death Stranding 2: On the Beach</a>, which releases in late June. After that comes <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/ghost-of-yotei/">Ghost of Yotei</a> in October.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
